Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.94,0:00:04.31,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:07.78,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're going to have \Nto go to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.78,0:00:11.91,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,I know that! I'm asking you to \Ndo something in the meantime!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:13.24,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.74,0:00:17.13,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Fugo, you aren't—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.54,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:22.01,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.09,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Staples!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.51,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,But wow, it actually closed up, \Njust like closing a comic book!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.51,0:00:30.04,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Narancia, could you wrap up his \Nstomach with masking tape now?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:30.95,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:33.51,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,You sure this isn't going to get infected?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:35.30,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:37.21,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, you know, I kinda like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.21,0:00:38.56,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Would you pipe down?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.25,0:00:42.35,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:46.69,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, we were able \Nto get to Capri safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.28,0:00:50.24,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Zucchero, who attacked us on the boat,\Nand the guy Mista handled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:53.65,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,are both passed out on the boat. \NNo need to worry about them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:58.37,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's hurry up and go to the place \Nwhere the ten billion lire is hidden!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.71,0:01:00.66,JoJo-main,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you hide it, Bucciarati?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:02.77,JoJo-main,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,A hidden safe at the bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:05.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you buried it \Nin a cave on the island?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.39,0:01:09.17,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Could you wait just a bit longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.69,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.69,0:01:14.05,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so worried about the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.91,0:01:15.51,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.16,0:01:22.31,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys. We're still \Nin here, so how 'bout it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.31,0:01:24.84,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do the cleaning later?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:28.42,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Does your name happen to be Toilette?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.07,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:36.70,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,If your name is actually Toilette, \Nthat would mean this is your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:40.00,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,You can boss around anyone \Nyou want in your own house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:45.20,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,But if that isn't the case, \Nyou've got no right to boss me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.22,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Hey, wait, dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.22,0:01:50.96,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear me? \NI said not to go in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.61,0:01:52.78,sign_2676_38_Crack,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Crack
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.22,0:01:59.84,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.36,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You want a piece of me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.70,0:02:01.36,JoJo-main,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:01.97,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,A new enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:04.22,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.22,0:02:05.14,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.85,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, stop Narancia!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.27,0:02:07.85,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why did you stop me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.85,0:02:09.71,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Could you be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.86,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,That voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.30,0:02:15.10,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears we've kept you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.90,0:02:18.15,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.64,0:02:22.35,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,This is Mr. Pericolo, \None of the capos of Passione.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:25.20,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I came to accept the ten billion lire,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.72,0:02:27.27,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:03.88,JoJo-EpTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(587,471)}Episodio 09 The First Mission from the Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:04.17,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I contacted him as soon \Nas we reached the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:08.39,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pericolo came all this \Nway to accept the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,One of Passione's capos...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:14.08,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for \Ncoming all this way, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:18.72,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,No, no. I'm the one who said I wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.17,0:04:21.15,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,All of you, lift your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:24.33,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You must be the newbie I heard about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.33,0:04:24.99,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.51,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati's told me all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.94,0:04:31.73,JoJo-main,Prei,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you've joined Passione, \Nyou're basically family.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:35.79,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You're free to call me Mr. Pericolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:37.96,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:42.18,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You, there. Sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.18,0:04:46.09,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,This one doesn't like being touched.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.62,0:04:47.54,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:48.75,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.00,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, "Yes, sir!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.00,0:04:51.31,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pericolo,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,why are you dressed up as a janitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.82,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,There's a perfectly good reason \Nfor this. I'll tell you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:05:01.11,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,More importantly, you do have it, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.11,0:05:04.95,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The ten billion lire to hand \Nover to the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:07.49,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.43,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,What? What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.43,0:05:11.49,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,He said it's right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:12.95,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.71,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.96,0:05:18.27,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,All I see are urinals...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.58,sign_7684_83_Plop,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Plop
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.03,JoJo-main,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was inside the urinal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:26.91,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's as safe as it gets, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.91,0:05:30.35,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks to be the guys who've been \Npeeing there this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.47,0:05:33.79,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Yup... It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:38.35,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,This necklace alone is worth at least \Nseven or eight hundred million.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.15,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:44.54,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I won't bother asking how \Nyou got this fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:49.24,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,All the organization cares about \Nis that you have the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:51.57,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you're already putting it away?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:53.80,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,C-Could I just touch it a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:55.70,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe even smell it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.71,0:06:04.13,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The reality this fortune shows us is that \Nthe owner is intelligent and trustworthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.00,0:06:06.73,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.73,0:06:10.59,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been promoted to the position of capo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:13.68,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hell, yeah! He's a capo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:17.14,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati's finally a capo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:23.61,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be taking over Polpo's \Nturf, now that he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:28.32,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be overseeing the \Ngambling, money-lending,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:33.62,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and smuggling at the harbor, as well \Nas the restaurants and hotels in Naples.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:39.46,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty percent of the profit will go to the \Norganization, and the other fifty will be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:41.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.41,0:06:43.55,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,He earned authority just like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.55,0:06:48.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,With Bucciarati's brains and popularity, \Nhe'll be rolling in the cash in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:54.51,JoJo-internal/narrator,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,But the ball suddenly started rolling \Nas soon as this newbie Giorno joined.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.08,0:06:56.89,JoJo-internal/narrator,mistA,0000,0000,0000,,Is he some kind of lucky boy or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.89,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:03.46,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I know you just took over for Polpo,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.95,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,but he had left one job unfinished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:15.31,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you'll be taking on any \Njobs that Polpo had, Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.61,0:07:17.71,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.71,0:07:20.05,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,A job that Polpo left unfinished?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.19,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,It's a direct order from the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:27.74,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,The... boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.74,0:07:28.86,JoJo-main,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,The boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.86,0:07:31.51,JoJo-main,Mista,0000,0000,0000,,The boss no one's ever met?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:33.93,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,An order... directly from him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.12,0:07:37.26,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. I'll tell you right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:45.29,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be guarding the boss's daughter, \Nand risking your lives doing so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.29,0:07:46.35,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.24,0:07:48.19,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.19,0:07:49.15,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,The boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:52.13,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Did you say "daughter"? \NThe boss has a daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.03,0:07:54.87,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The boss we were eventually going to \Ntrack down and defeat has a daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:59.70,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,You'll start guarding her right now. \NI've handed her over to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.50,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Handed her over?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.04,0:08:04.04,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.95,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Could that guy be...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.45,0:08:08.96,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,No, not "guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.35,0:08:11.55,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,She must be the boss's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.43,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,That's her?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.78,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mind if I go to the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.77,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine, Trish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.24,0:08:25.52,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,For now, stay by her side.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.80,0:08:27.82,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,The order is already in effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.89,0:08:30.23,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:36.21,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Trish Una, \Nand she's fifteen years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.64,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,"Una" is her mother's maiden name, \Nnot the boss's family name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:45.79,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Trish hasn't met the boss once in her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:51.71,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati, as you're well aware, \Nno one knows who the boss is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.71,0:08:58.05,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, even the boss has a past, \Nespecially when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:06.81,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Two months ago, a woman named \NDonatella died of illness in Calabria.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.47,0:09:14.56,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,A few days before her death, she asked \Nthat a man named Solido Naso be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.28,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,That man was Trish's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:23.33,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she was just trying to look \Nout for her daughter's well-being,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.87,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:27.71,JoJo-main,bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Naso doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.71,0:09:32.74,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that was one of the aliases \Nthat the boss used when he was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.01,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.52,0:09:38.72,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Beware of anyone trying to \Nlook into the name Naso.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:44.71,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone with any status in Passione \Nis very cautious about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.73,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Just trying to look into \Nthe boss's past would mean
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.73,0:09:50.19,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,challenging the organization itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:54.14,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Word about Donatella eventually spread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.14,0:09:57.88,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Word spread even more when it \Ncame out that she had a daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:10:01.36,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, the boss \Ncaught wind of this, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.83,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The boss's decision was immediate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.23,0:10:08.29,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Through a few other men, \Nhe gave me the order
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.29,0:10:12.42,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,and placed her in my custody \Nsoon after her mother's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:15.88,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The boss must've known immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.40,0:10:20.08,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't know she existed until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:24.43,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,but he knew for a fact that \NTrish was indeed his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.17,0:10:28.14,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,And right after I took Trish into my custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:33.19,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,we found out that someone was after her life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.19,0:10:36.07,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,If the boss's order had come \Neven thirty minutes later,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:39.98,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Trish most likely would've been \Nkidnapped by them, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:43.25,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:46.33,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Who's after her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:48.74,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,People who have betrayed the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.74,0:10:51.16,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know how many of them there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:55.71,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,They're trying to defeat the boss and \Ntake over his drug trafficking routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:56.96,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Drugs...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.32,0:11:02.37,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,They're under the impression that \NTrish knows a secret about the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.57,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,They want information so that \Nthey can defeat the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:12.20,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,But Trish is just a frail \Nlittle girl who knows nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.59,0:11:14.36,JoJo-main,Bruno,0000,0000,0000,,How long will we be guarding her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:18.61,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,One week... Actually, \Nit could even be less.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:22.65,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,It's just until the boss finds those \Ntraitors and gets rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:27.16,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,Leave this island immediately \Nand hide her somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:31.27,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who know that Trish \Nis with you are the boss and myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:32.58,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Pericolo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.91,0:11:37.05,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,You said that order was supposed \Nto go to Polpo, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:39.05,JoJo-main,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:41.30,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,The enemies are Stand users...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:45.01,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I'd say that's a safe assumption.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.39,0:11:49.58,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,They're most likely moving as a team, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:52.23,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,We don't yet know how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.96,0:11:55.34,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a Stand ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.34,0:11:58.11,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all I can do for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:12:01.31,JoJo-main,Peri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact you again if \NI learn anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.07,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.07,0:12:18.96,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.96,0:12:22.25,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Is it with you... um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:26.55,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I going to be with you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:29.62,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.15,0:12:32.50,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be all six of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:35.77,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,We will be risking our lives to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:36.88,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.64,0:12:41.49,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would you mind taking off that jacket?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:44.99,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,My jacket? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:47.10,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Just hurry up and take it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:50.20,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if I want to see \Nyou shirtless or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.44,JoJo-main,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:58.40,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a handkerchief, \Nso go buy one for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:02.98,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Also, some stockings and \NGivenchy Blush No. 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.98,0:13:06.55,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,The stockings need to be \Nreinforced at the thighs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.79,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,Get the latest issue of {\i1}Italian Vogue{\i0}, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.79,0:13:10.35,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,and some mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:15.03,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather die than drink one \Nthat's not from France, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:19.17,JoJo-main,Trish,0000,0000,0000,,When you're done gawking at the \Nscenery, go buy that stuff for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.74,0:13:25.63,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,Guard the boss's daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.30,0:13:32.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,So we suddenly have a connection to the \Nmysterious boss that I've been looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.91,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.31,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,If we can see this through,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.31,0:13:41.21,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati will be able to gain the \Nsame level of trust that Polpo had.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:45.06,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,But if we fail, it'll mean our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.29,JoJo-internal/narrator,Gio,0000,0000,0000,,All six of us are well aware of that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:56.27,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem? Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.58,0:13:58.84,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying to pet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.48,0:14:01.52,sign_20128_222_At_9_25_this_mor,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,At 9:25 this morning at Naples Prison, Polpo shot himself in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.27,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:05.49,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Quit struggling! I can't read it. Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.32,0:14:13.29,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,"At 9:25 this morning at Naples Prison, \NPolpo shot himself in the head."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:18.19,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Well, damn... I was sure it'd be Polpo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:20.50,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:25.15,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one guarding \NTrish, who disappeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:28.21,sign_20803_229_Find_them,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Find them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:29.37,sign_20803_229_Find_them,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(392,293)}Find them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.10,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.53,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,"Find them," eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.53,0:14:38.77,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,But was anyone as reliable as Polpo?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.16,0:14:44.02,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Only a capo would be tasked \Nwith such an important job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.02,0:14:47.48,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,And someone with Stand abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:51.70,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else like that exist?
