Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.09,0:15:04.96,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,And that's it for shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.77,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Surroundings are all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.77,0:15:09.38,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:14.18,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I go this way and turn here, \NI'll end up back on this street,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:16.64,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,and then head in the opposite direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:18.64,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.90,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Narancia, listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.90,0:15:30.74,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,That's a list of food and other \Nthings you need to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:33.03,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,These are the keys to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:35.81,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,You can do this, Narancia.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.81,0:15:37.62,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.01,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.45,0:15:43.93,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully. No one knows \Nanyone is at this hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.93,0:15:46.92,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,not even the people at the winery \Nin the vineyard out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.42,0:15:52.63,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're done shopping, try going in \Ncircles on the same path over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:55.46,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Also try U-turning every once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.75,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Check to see if anyone's following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.75,0:16:01.62,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Then, come home after \Nswitching over to the other car
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.62,0:16:05.65,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,that I arranged just in case \Nin one of the city's parking lots.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:09.65,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,No one else knows that we're \Nguarding the boss's daughter,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:16.16,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,but if someone's looking for us, the last \Nthing we want them to do is follow us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:17.43,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.15,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone needs to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.15,0:16:20.62,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:24.42,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,But we have to make absolutely sure \Nno one finds out about this hideo—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.42,0:16:26.90,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, I get it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.76,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.76,0:16:32.52,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now repeat all the steps I just \Nexplained to you from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.52,0:16:33.22,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.06,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Once I'm done shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.06,0:16:39.47,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,I drive around in circles \Nin the vineyard out there—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:39.47,sign_23951_276_Jab,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,J{\c&H7667DA&}a{\c&H9D2CD3&}b
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:41.02,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:45.49,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong! Quit messing around! \NAgain, from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.49,0:16:46.37,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.37,0:16:47.74,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.31,0:16:50.99,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Drive around so I don't get dizzy—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.46,0:16:50.97,sign_24227_282_Jab,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,J{\c&H73529F&}a{\c&H935787&}b
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:53.70,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Urgh! What the hell is your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:55.58,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Abbacchio!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.58,0:16:57.98,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to stop jabbing \Nme with the damn keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.98,0:17:00.20,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than him, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:01.61,JoJo-flashback,Fugo,0000,0000,0000,,Letting him go shopping is a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:06.26,JoJo-flashback,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,You two will have to figure out whether \Nor not you should be jabbed on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.26,0:17:13.17,JoJo-flashback,Abba,0000,0000,0000,,But with Narancia's Stand ability, he should \Nbe able to stop anyone tailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.17,0:17:16.27,JoJo-flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why Bucciarati \Nordered him to go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:22.06,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,So basically, that means I just need to make \Nsure I'm not followed back here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:24.26,JoJo-flashback,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,By anyone who might follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:31.40,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.82,0:17:34.23,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't look like anyone's following me,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.23,0:17:36.49,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,but something feels off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:42.98,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about switching over \Nto the other car that Fugo prepared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:45.83,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:49.62,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Come on already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:54.47,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Where exactly are you headed, huh, Narancia?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.47,0:17:55.63,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,That came from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:06.02,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so, where are you headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.28,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,You keep looking behind you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.90,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you being followed or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:13.98,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?! Get outta the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.19,0:18:15.04,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, talk about scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:17.59,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one asking the questions here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.59,0:18:21.16,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Don't answer a question with \Nanother question. That's rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.04,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get the hell out \Nof my car, you dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.18,0:18:27.22,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,You're not leaving me with any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:29.40,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Formaggio.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.40,0:18:30.92,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a member of the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.41,0:18:34.96,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,You already know that Polpo \Ndied yesterday, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:43.74,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Yet everyone on your team just \Nhappened to disappear at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:41.14,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Shit... He's bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.65,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't know the truth, \Nbut he's definitely after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:47.56,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Right when I had something important \Nto discuss with you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.65,0:18:47.56,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is he a Stand user?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:52.13,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Narancia, I finally managed to \Nfind you, but why are they gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.98,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Bucciarati and the rest of your squad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.03,0:18:57.23,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:59.83,JoJo-main,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea where they are right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.62,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Did you check the \Nrestaurants around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.62,0:19:02.99,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,This car...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:04.63,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,It's a rental, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:06.50,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Bucciarati was the one who rented it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:10.00,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,If you didn't know that, \Nwhy the hell are you in this car?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:11.00,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:15.28,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I-I always drive around \Nin Bucciarati's cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.22,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm seventeen, so I don't \Nhave my own car yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:19.84,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm borrowing his.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.63,0:19:23.63,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:28.77,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the mortician is trying to figure \Nout how the hell to cremate Polpo's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.77,0:19:32.05,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,They can't figure out how to get \Nhis body into the furnace.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:37.35,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,They're just gonna have to chop him \Nup into tiny pieces, aren't they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.48,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.48,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you think so, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.96,0:19:48.82,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.54,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? Th-There's no one here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.54,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,You actually fell for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.50,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Man, you're useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:02.59,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Narancia, why are you guys
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.59,0:20:06.31,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,hiding somewhere when \Na capo's funeral is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:10.77,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna make you talk \Nif I can't just follow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:10.77,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now you've done it, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.77,0:20:13.58,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna tell me all kinds \Nof things, right here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.58,0:20:15.05,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.05,0:20:15.73,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.61,0:20:18.69,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.19,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll murder you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:30.87,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:32.71,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Li'l Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:37.09,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,So he's a Stand user... Tiny Feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.70,sign_29718_353_Buda_Buda_Buda,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,Ba{\c&H41B3FA&}da {\c&H3F6DF3&\4c&H7CB4AD&}Ba{\c&H41B3FA&}da {\c&H3F6DF3&\4c&H7CB4AD&}Ba{\c&H41B3FA&}da
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.06,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.06,0:20:46.51,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Look at how badly I'm bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.51,0:20:48.63,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?! How dare you?! How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.53,0:20:48.21,sign_29718_353_Buda_Buda_Buda,Sfx,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3F94CF&\4c&H302C77&}Bada Bada Bada
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:50.68,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.48,0:20:55.48,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,This is definitely not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.90,0:20:58.98,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:01.40,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.40,0:21:03.34,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.56,0:21:07.41,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shit! He's out of his goddamn mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:09.54,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,He's lost it and is shooting anything in sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm stuck in this narrow \Ncar with nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.08,0:21:15.42,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,That's the most dangerous part of all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.68,0:21:19.09,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,A-A bomb?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:21.84,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Murder him, Li'l Bomber!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:25.84,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,How do you like that? \NAnd that?! And that?! And that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.84,0:21:27.30,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Are you dead yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.25,0:21:30.53,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.47,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.17,0:21:33.85,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:36.30,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Did the blast blow him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:39.29,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,But... there's not even a \Nshred of his corpse left!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:41.73,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:46.32,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on... I'm right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.37,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I can make myself small.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:52.13,JoJo-internal/narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:58.39,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Tiny Feet... All the other guys \Nsay this ability is worthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:03.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,What determines if something is worthless \Nor not is how you use your brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.80,0:22:05.47,JoJo-internal/narrator,Form,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is with abilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.47,0:22:08.55,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell? I don't see him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:11.60,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,How the hell?! Damn it, where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.60,0:22:12.93,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Is he here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:16.69,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,The same thing happened when \Nhe first showed up in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.35,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck in your search.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.69,0:22:19.88,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Where the hell did he just pop up from?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:22.70,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be buying some time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.36,0:22:22.96,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Now he's hiding somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.26,0:22:28.70,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.70,0:22:32.05,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,This bastard's bought stuff for a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.05,0:22:36.41,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Stockings and blush...\NAnd it's high-end blush to boot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.41,0:22:38.14,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he shopping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.14,0:22:41.69,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for his mom or his older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.69,0:22:45.20,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,No... Chicks are super picky \Nabout what they like,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.20,0:22:47.60,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,so they buy fashion and \Nmakeup stuff on their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.60,0:22:50.30,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,The only chick who'd have \Na guy buy stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:54.43,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,is a chick who can't leave \Nher place for some reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.43,0:22:56.91,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,This is becoming more and more suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.91,0:23:00.02,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my gut feeling was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.29,0:23:02.24,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, without a doubt,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.24,0:23:06.32,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,the one who was ordered to guard \Nthe boss's daughter is Bucciarati!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:11.32,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll make sure I get Narancia \Nto show me where they're hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.32,0:23:15.97,JoJo-main,Form,0000,0000,0000,,My ability should start working \Non him at any moment now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.75,0:23:21.08,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it... That bastard's definitely \Nsomewhere around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.08,0:23:24.12,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he plans to follow \Nme all the way back.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:25.80,JoJo-internal/narrator,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.73,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna find him and kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.73,0:23:31.01,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to make it back \Nwithout getting followed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.40,JoJo-main,Nara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to follow the orders I was given!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:41.26,JoJo-NextTitle,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(984,1)}Episodio 10\N\NHitman Team
